South Carolina Walkability Index

sc_walkability_index.Rd

The dataset of measures from the US EPA's National Walkability Index for SC block groups

sc_walkability_index

Format

A data frame with 3059 rows and 30 columns

geoid10

Census Block Group 12-digit FIPS Code (2010)

geoid20

Census Block Group 12-digit FIPS Code (2018)

statefp

State FIPS Code

countyf

County FIPS Code

tractce

Tract FIPS Code

blockgrpc

Block Group FIPS Code

csa

Combined Statistical Area Code

csa_nam

Combined Statistical Area Name

cbsa

Core-Based Statistical Area Code

cbsa_nm

Core-Based Statistical Area Name

ac_totl

Total Geometric Area of Block Group

ac_watr

Total Water Area

ac_land

Total Land Area

ac_unpr

Total Unprotexted Land Area

tot_pop

Total Population

count_hu

Housing Units

hh

Households

workers

Count of Workers

d2b_e8mixa

Employment Mix

d2a_ephhm

Employment and Household Mix

d3b

Intersection Density

d4a

Proximity to Transit Stops

d2b_rnk

Employment Mix Ranking (1-20)

d2a_rnk

Employment and Household Mix Ranking (1-20)

d3b_rnk

Intersection Density Ranking (1-20)

d4a_rnk

Proximity to Transit Stops Ranking (1-20)

nt_wlk_in

National Walkability Index Score

shp_lng

Shape Perimeter

shap_ar

Shape Area

geometry

Geometry

Source
